{
  "texts": [
    "This sets the ground for the user to discover their targets of interest.",
    "• DC2: Progressive Disclosure (T1, T2, T3).",
    "To facilitate incremental sensemaking, it is important to support users to drill down from a high-level overview to intermediate abstractions.",
    "This includes disclosure of a specific topic's sub-structure, the containing documents, and the occurrences of keywords.",
    "It not only supports a better understanding of the topics and keywords but also directs users to find the target of interest."
  ]
}